# OpenAI API Configuration (Optional)
# Get your API key from: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk_your_api_key_here

# Gemini API Configuration (Recommended - Free Tier Available)
# Get your API key from: https://aistudio.google.com/
GEMINI_API_KEY=your_gemini_api_key_here

# Important: 
# 1. Create a .env.local file (not .env.local.example)
# 2. Copy this format and paste your actual API keys
# 3. Never commit .env.local to git - it's already in .gitignore
# 4. The chatbot will automatically fall back to a local smart responder if no keys are provided or if quotas are exceeded.
